FT  17 AUG 94 / World News in Brief: London Kurds jailed for bomb campaign:
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Three Kurdish terrorists from north London who launched a bombing campaign
against Turkish targets in Britain were jailed at the Old Bailey for terms
ranging from 12 to 15 years.
