FT  15 AUG 94 / Equity Markets: Other Markets - Frankfurt
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Market professionals have been looking forward eagerly to the second-quarter
reports from the 'big three' chemical groups, with BASF kicking off on
Thursday, and Bayer and Hoechst due next week. A Goldman Sachs report on the
