FT  15 AUG 94 / Business Travel: Israel to Nigeria
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Israel's national airline, El Al, will commence direct flights to Nigeria in
the next two weeks.
The two countries re-established diplomatic relations about three years ago
after a 19-year break.
