<HEADLINE>
FT  15 AUG 94 / Business Travel: Air Maroc strike
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Royal Air Maroc services have been badly disrupted by a strike over the
sacking of a pilot. The strike by air crews entered its fifth day on
Saturday, according to the air crew union, the AMPT.
There have been no negotiations with the airline, according to the union.
